Would just like to point out that this isn't condoning the murder of hundreds of people...  This &quot;fatwa&quot; is calling for the execution of a SINGLE person; apparently the leaders believe that by killing the person who wrote the article, that will excise some of the anger of their people.  Calling for the execution of a single person to get the citizens to stop killing hundreds is hardly a stamp of approval...  It's a last ditch effort for those in control to get their citizens back in line before they have to resort to military tactics and such.<br>
<br>
Obviously, it's wrong to kill the person who wrote the article in the first place, and it's horrid that the people in the region became so outraged by this.  These people need to learn to let things like this slide off their backa.<br>
